{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":868,"text":"The most complex problems in our time"},{"time":4196,"text":"can be solved with simple techniques,"},{"time":7166,"text":"if we are able to dream."}]},{"cues":[{"time":10991,"text":"As a child, I discovered\nthat creativity is the key"},{"time":15976,"text":"to cross from dreams to reality."},{"time":21570,"text":"I learned this from my grandmother,"},{"time":23907,"text":"Dr. Ruth Tichauer,"},{"time":26300,"text":"a Jewish refugee that settled\nin the heart of the Andes."},{"time":31729,"text":"That is how I grew up:"},{"time":34442,"text":"encouraged to see beyond any limitation."},{"time":38982,"text":"So part of my education\nincluded helping her"},{"time":42430,"text":"in remote, indigenous communities."},{"time":45864,"text":"I cherish those memories,"},{"time":48113,"text":"because they helped me\nto understand life outside the city,"},{"time":55040,"text":"a life with a lot of possibilities,"},{"time":58418,"text":"without barriers, as language or culture."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61780,"text":"During those trips, my grandmother\nused to recite a Kipling poem:"},{"time":66687,"text":"\"Something hidden. Go and find it."},{"time":70296,"text":"Go and look behind the Mountains."},{"time":72978,"text":"Something lost behind the mountains."},{"time":76757,"text":"Lost and waiting for you. Go!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":81624,"text":"In the coming years,\nI became a medical student."},{"time":86299,"text":"One of every hundred\nchildren born worldwide"},{"time":91547,"text":"has some kind of heart disease."},{"time":95214,"text":"There's a part of this problem\nI think I can solve --"},{"time":100388,"text":"the part of this problem\nI have spent my life working on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":107904,"text":"The problem starts"},{"time":110279,"text":"during pregnancy."},{"time":112610,"text":"The fetus needs to survive\ninside the mother."},{"time":116808,"text":"Survival depends on communication"},{"time":121321,"text":"between the systemic\nand the pulmonary blood."},{"time":124994,"text":"At the moment of birth,"},{"time":127055,"text":"this communication needs to stop."},{"time":130474,"text":"If it doesn't close, the baby\nhas a hole in the heart."},{"time":135398,"text":"It is caused by prematurity\nand genetic conditions."},{"time":140537,"text":"But what we know today"},{"time":143556,"text":"is that a lack of oxygen\nis also one of the causes."},{"time":149119,"text":"As you can see in the chart,"},{"time":151775,"text":"the frequency of this kind of hole"},{"time":156387,"text":"dramatically increases with altitude."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160327,"text":"Video: (Baby crying)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164357,"text":"When you look at patients\nwith this condition,"},{"time":167649,"text":"they seem desperate to breathe."},{"time":170521,"text":"To close the hole, major surgery\nused to be the only solution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176527,"text":"One night, my friend Malte,\nwere camping in the Amazon region."},{"time":182385,"text":"The only thing that would not burn\nin the fire was a green avocado branch."},{"time":189088,"text":"Then came a moment of inspiration."},{"time":192513,"text":"So we used the branch as a mold\nfor our first invention."},{"time":197110,"text":"The holes in children's hearts\ncan be closed with it."},{"time":200509,"text":"A coil is a piece of wire\nwrapped onto itself."},{"time":205313,"text":"It maybe doesn't look so fancy to you now,"},{"time":208760,"text":"but that was our first successful attempt"},{"time":212989,"text":"to create a device for this major problem."},{"time":217671,"text":"In this video, we can see\nhow a very tiny catheter"},{"time":220832,"text":"takes the coil to the heart."},{"time":223393,"text":"The coil then closes the hole."},{"time":225721,"text":"After that moment of inspiration,"},{"time":228550,"text":"there came a very long time of effort"},{"time":234533,"text":"developing a prototype."},{"time":236495,"text":"In vitro and in vivo studies took\nthousands of hours of work in the lab."},{"time":243321,"text":"The coil, if it works, can save lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248202,"text":"I returned from Germany to Bolivia,"},{"time":250638,"text":"thinking that wherever we go,"},{"time":253166,"text":"we have the opportunity\nto make a difference."},{"time":257278,"text":"With my wife and partner,\nDr. Alexandra Heath,"},{"time":261802,"text":"we started to see patients."},{"time":263492,"text":"After successfully treating\npatients with our coil,"},{"time":267817,"text":"we felt really enthusiastic."},{"time":270688,"text":"But we live in a place"},{"time":274554,"text":"that is 12,000 feet high."},{"time":279694,"text":"And,"},{"time":282284,"text":"the patients there need a special device\nto solve their heart condition."},{"time":287865,"text":"The hole in altitude\npatients is different,"},{"time":290352,"text":"because the orifice\nbetween the arteries is larger."},{"time":294479,"text":"Most patients cannot afford\nto be treated on time,"},{"time":299405,"text":"and they die."},{"time":301973,"text":"The first coil could successfully treat"},{"time":305616,"text":"only half of the patients in Bolivia."},{"time":311577,"text":"The search started again."},{"time":314942,"text":"We went back to the drawing board."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319574,"text":"After many trials,"},{"time":321031,"text":"and with the help of my grandmother's\nindigenous friends in the mountains,"},{"time":326078,"text":"we obtained a new device."},{"time":328753,"text":"For centuries, indigenous women\ntold stories by weaving complex patterns"},{"time":334631,"text":"on looms,"},{"time":336262,"text":"and an unexpected skill\nhelped us for the new device."},{"time":341673,"text":"We take this traditional method of weaving"},{"time":344507,"text":"and make a design made by a smart material"},{"time":348927,"text":"that records shape."},{"time":351236,"text":"It seems this time,"},{"time":353755,"text":"the weaving allows us\nto create a seamless device"},{"time":358506,"text":"that doesn't rust"},{"time":361072,"text":"because it's made of only one piece."},{"time":365427,"text":"It can change by itself\ninto very complex structures"},{"time":369931,"text":"by a procedure that took\ndecades to develop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374903,"text":"As you can see, the device enters the body"},{"time":377746,"text":"through the natural channels."},{"time":380173,"text":"Doctors have only to close\nthe catheter through the hole."},{"time":384104,"text":"Our device expands, places itself"},{"time":386972,"text":"and closes the hole."},{"time":390375,"text":"We have this beautiful delivery system"},{"time":393315,"text":"that is so simple to use"},{"time":395383,"text":"because it works by itself."},{"time":398422,"text":"No open surgery was necessary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":403494,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":412006,"text":"As doctors, we fight with diseases"},{"time":414713,"text":"that take a long time\nand effort to heal -- if they do."},{"time":419443,"text":"This is the child from before,"},{"time":422100,"text":"after the procedure."},{"time":423780,"text":"As you can see --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":425423,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":430007,"text":"As you can see,\nonce the device is in place,"},{"time":433130,"text":"the patient is 100 percent healed."},{"time":436622,"text":"From start to finish,"},{"time":438075,"text":"the whole procedure takes only 30 minutes."},{"time":443183,"text":"That's very rewarding from the medical\nand human point of view."},{"time":448444,"text":"We are so proud that some\nof our former patients"},{"time":455011,"text":"are part of our team --"},{"time":458643,"text":"a team, thanks to added close interaction"},{"time":462491,"text":"with patients that work with us."},{"time":465799,"text":"Together, we have only one idea:"},{"time":469103,"text":"the best solutions need to be simple."},{"time":473530,"text":"We lost the fear\nof creating something new."}]},{"cues":[{"time":477523,"text":"The path, it's not easy."},{"time":480191,"text":"Many obstacles arise all the time."},{"time":483934,"text":"But we receive strength from our patients."},{"time":487971,"text":"Their resilience and courage"},{"time":492233,"text":"inspire our creativity."},{"time":495311,"text":"Our goal is to make sure"},{"time":498282,"text":"that no child is left behind,"},{"time":502360,"text":"not because of cost or access."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507367,"text":"So we have to start a foundation"},{"time":510355,"text":"with a one-to-one model."},{"time":513831,"text":"We will give one device for free"},{"time":517061,"text":"to make sure that every child is treated."},{"time":521600,"text":"We are in many countries now,"},{"time":524482,"text":"but we need to be everywhere."},{"time":528926,"text":"This whole thing began"},{"time":531931,"text":"with one impossible idea"},{"time":534819,"text":"as will continue it, really:"},{"time":538698,"text":"No child is left behind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543670,"text":"Muchas gracias."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545498,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}